A limitation of the current study is that all the participants were recruited from the same hospital, which may affect the generalizability of the results. However, our sample is gender-representative of the Polish population. According to data from the Central Statistical Office in Poland (GUS) for 2023, women constitute 51.6% of the population, which is comparable to the studied group (53.5%). Our sample is slightly older (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
